pointsandrectanlgeslab

Class APRectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • pointsandrectanlgeslab.APRectangle

  • public class APRectangle
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a rectangle to be drawn in a Graphics window. The Rectangle has APPoint top left corner, width, and height.
